FBIS4-55595 "dreeu096_i_94014" FBIS-EEU-94-096 Daily Report 17 May 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Croats Urge Serbs To Join Federation Croats Urge Serbs To Join Federation LD1705201494 Zagreb HTV Television in Serbo-Croatian 1730 GMT 17 May 94 LD1705201494 Zagreb HTV Television Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] At a news conference in Zagreb, the Croat National Council of Bosnia-Herzegovina [HNV] spoke of an initiative for the founding of a commission for monitoring the implementation of the Washington and Vienna agreements between the Croats and Muslims. The HNV also appealed to the Serb people in Bosnia-Herzegovina to join this agreement on Bosnia-Herzegovina as a state belonging to three equal nations, refrain from violence and ethnic cleansing, stop the war, and return territories taken by force.
